casebody.data:
Larry HOLLOWAY, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
TOWNSHIP OF JACKSON, and Township of Jackson Zoning Board of Adjustment, Defendants-Respondents. C-352 September Term 2018
081730 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 16, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002963-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
